<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-12-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-12-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="558" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d558">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51W89 Poland/96</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Polish Embassy</gloss> to
                                    the <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>The Polish Government has the honour to acknowledge receipt of the
                                note of the United States Government of December 15th, 1932.</p>
                            <p>The Polish Government holds itself fully at the disposal of the
                                United States Government for the survey of the problem of Poland’s
                                war debt to the United States with a view to safeguarding the
                                general interests of our two countries.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <dateline rendition="#left">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-12-21">December 21, 1932</date>.</dateline>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>